### reset panel dafault ###

==> shutdown this panel first:
$ xfce4-panel --quit
==> kill the xfce4 configuration daemon:
$ pkill xfconfd
==> first delete setting for the panel:
$ rm -rf ~/.config/xfce4/panel
==> clear out the setting forxfconfd:
$ rm -rf ~/.config/xfce4/xfconf/xfce-perchannel-xml/xfce4-panel.xml
==> restart the panel,run 
$ xfce4-panel

source : https://forums.linuxmint.com/viewtopic.php?t=297772
